# Feature: Tập với PT (Book a Personal Trainer)

## Overview
Add a PT booking flow from the home screen:
Home → Calendar (4 weeks) → Time Picker → PT List → Booking confirmation

## User Flow
1. Tap "Tập với PT" button on home screen
2. Calendar screen shows 4 weeks from today
   - Days with PT availability highlighted in orange/accent
   - Other days dimmed
3. After selecting a date → time picker appears (start + end time, 5-min increments)
4. After selecting time → scrollable PT cards shown
5. If no PT available → "Rất tiếc" message

## Architecture (Future-friendly)

### Data Layer (`pt-data.js`)
- `PT_PROFILES[]` - PT info (id, name, specialty, experience, rating, avatar, bio)
- `PT_SCHEDULES{}` - Keyed by PT id, with:
  - `recurring` - Weekly recurring availability (day-of-week → time slots)
  - `overrides` - Specific date overrides (date string → slots or null for blocked)
- Helper functions:
  - `getAvailableDatesInRange(startDate, endDate)` → dates with any PT
  - `getAvailablePTs(date, startTime, endTime)` → PT profiles available
  - `isPTAvailable(ptId, date, startTime, endTime)` → boolean

### UI Components
- Calendar grid (reusable, week-based)
- Time picker (two selects: start/end, 5-min steps)
- PT card (avatar + profile, horizontal scroll)

